    "body" : "<p>According to java,</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>Data Type          -         Default values</p>\n  \n  <p>byte                    -          0</p>\n  \n  <p>short                 -        0</p>\n  \n  <p>int                     -          0</p>\n  \n  <p>long                    -          0L</p>\n  \n  <p>float                  -           0.0f</p>\n  \n  <p>double             -                   0.0d</p>\n  \n  <p>char                      -        '\\u0000'</p>\n  \n  <p>String (or any object)    -    null</p>\n  \n  <p>boolean                 -              false</p>\n</blockquote>\n"
  }, {
